    "body": "Hardcoding a wide dialog that still doesn't understand the message size is bad for polish, and currently just duplicates the existing message prompt behaviour.  As requested above, please make the dialog resize to fit the message width if it is less than a defined (in the widget yaml) maximum, and use `WidgetUtils.TruncateText` if the message is longer.  This is also a notification dialog, so should use \"Ok\" instead of cancel.\n"
